729126f-a.title: Richmond: Manor Road - Windsor Road
729126f-a.text:
Manor Road, at the S. E. corner of Windsor Road. The
house is the home of Dristrict Attorney Fach of Richmond County
and bears street number 663. The house and barns were formerly
part of the Reon Barnes estate.
June 5, 1930
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

729109f-a.title: Richmond: Manor Road - Windsor Road
729109f-a.text:
663 Manor Road, east side, 50 yards south of Windsor Road,
ahowing the A. C. Fach residence. It was formerly (1898 to 1917 maps)
the Reon Barnes house.
April 22, 1932
P. L. Sperr
